description: Original Title: Pearl Jam - Let's Play Two Release Year: 2017 Video Quality: BD-25 Video Codec: AVC Audio Codec: DTS-HD MA 5.1 Resolution: 1920 × 1080 https://www.imdb.com/title/tt7435110/ Let's Play Two brings together the audio recording of Pearl Jam's live performances at Wrigley Field in Chicago in 2016. The project, which will also be released on film, brings together the biggest hits in the group's catalog over the course of its 25-year career , in 17 tracks. "Light Light", "Better Man", "Lightning Bold" are some of the songs that make up the album, in addition to the classic 'Black,' Jeremy 'and' Alive '. The show shows the special relationship between the band, the city of Chicago - hometown of vocalist Eddie Vedder - and the stadium that is historically marked by numerous historical moments of the sports and music world. 1.
